room_title: Escape room "Chef Olivieri Rescue" by The Mansion Escape Room in Tallahassee
room_description:
Step into Chef Olivieri’s Restaurant for a dining experience you will not soon forget. The once renowned restaurant, founded by the brilliant young Chef Olivieri, has been overtaken by undead ghouls and abandoned in the chaos of The Outbreak.
Our search and rescue team has recently intercepted radio transmissions from deep within Chef Olivieri’s establishment. You and your team of rescuers are tasked with locating the lone survivor and bringing him to safety. Will you succeed in your mission, or find yourselves on the menu?
